    <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_">To add a dimension or locate a Point:</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Interface2">Method 1<text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">: </text><text styleclass="Interface">Part-Editor</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">: Add dimensions and constraints - see </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Geometry-Dimension" anchor="DimensionPoint" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">Add Dimension</link></para>
          <para styleclass="Interface2">OR</para>
          <para styleclass="Interface2">Method 2<text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">: </text><text styleclass="Interface">Mechanism-Editor</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">: Use </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-FunctionBlock-PointProperties" anchor="PointPosition" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">Point Properties dialog</link><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"> &gt; </text><text styleclass="Parameter">Lock and Edit here </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Interface2">OR</para>
          <para styleclass="Interface2">Method 3: <text styleclass="Interface">Mechanism-Editor</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">: </text><text styleclass="Body Text">Drag a </text><text styleclass="Element">Point</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> if it has no constraints or dimensions and it has a </text><text styleclass="Element">Trace-Point </text><text styleclass="SeeAlso">- see </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-AddTracePoint" anchor="DragaTrace-Point" styleclass="SeeAlso">Add Trace-Point</link></para>
